The video below is copyright free and can be used at will, without asking for authorization Watch the video The inaugural African Schools Champions Cup takes place this weekend at Stade des Martyrs in Kinshasa, giving boys and girls schools teams from six African member associations the chance to improve through exposure to competition and from social and education development programmes. As the first three teams touched down in the Congo DR capital, representatives from preview the tournament in this video submission.  Mlambo Sabelo – South Africa
Pierette Chigblo – Benin
Shiko Lethlhogonolo – South Africa Girls’ coach
Victor Sagbo – Benin
Ntombifuthi Khumalo – South Africa Boys’ coach
